Calculate performance metrics.

Calculate performance metrics.

getperf(MSE)

Arguments

MSE
an object of class MSE

Value

a list n stocks long each with a data frame of performance metrics (columns) by management procedure (row) MSE.

  • Y10. Mean yield over the first 10 years of the projection
  • Y20. Mean yield over years 11-20 of the projection
  • Y30. Mean yield over years 21-30 of the projection
  • PGK. Probability of Green Kobe (F<FMSY AND B>BMSY) region over all years of the projection
  • POF. Probability of Over-Fishing (F>FMSY) over all years of the projection
  • POFed. Probability of Over-Fished status (B<BMSY) over all years of the projection
  • D10. Mean depletion (SSB relative to unfished) over the first 10 years of the projection
  • D20. Mean depletion (SSB relative to unfished) over years 11-20 of the projection
  • D30. Mean depletion (SSB relative to unfished) over years 21-30 of the projection
  • LD. Mean depletion (SSB relative to unfished) over all projected years
  • RSSB. Mean Spawning Stock Biomass in final projection year relative to zero fishing
  • LRSSB. Mean Spawning Stock Biomass over all projection years relative to zero fishing
  • AAVY. Mean Average Annual Variability in Yield over all projections
  • carat. weight of the diamond (0.2--5.01) ...
